   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "gs_title",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "# TensorBinding.jl — Getting Started\n",
    "\n",
    "Minimal 1D walk-through of the core API:\n",
    "\n",
    "1. **1D chain** — `get_bands`, `get_ldos_spatial`, `get_dos_stochastic`\n",
    "2. **`add_onsite!`** — on-site potential\n",
    "3. **`add_hopping!`** — generic (NNN) hopping\n",
    "4. **`add_zeeman!`** — spin + Zeeman field\n",
    "5. **`add_soc!`** — Rashba spin-orbit coupling\n",
    "6. **`add_superconductivity!`** — s-wave BdG (Nambu doubling)\n",
    "7. **`get_scf`** - simple scf calculation\n",
    "\n",
    "Each section builds on a `L=6` chain (`N=64` sites) and shows bands, spatial\n",
    "LDOS, and DoS in a single 1x3 figure. No auxiliary-index projections are applied;\n",
    "see `aux_ldos_examples.ipynb` and `momentum_spectral_functions.ipynb` for\n",
    "spin/Nambu/sublattice-resolved spectra."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 3,
   "id": "gs_imports",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "name": "stderr",
     "output_type": "stream",
     "text": [
      "WARNING: replacing module TensorBinding.\n"
     ]
    }
